Description:Jewish books program
 Orayta is a open-source,
 cross platform jewish books project, based on "תורת אמת".
 Orayta ("Torah" in Aramaic),
 intends to give simple access to as many Jewish sources as possible, 
 from the Bible, Mishna and Talmud,
 to books written in the last years, freely and off-line.
 Find us at: http://orayta.googlecode.com/
